Welcome to the **rust** service agent.

Plain Rust service built on Cargo. Use this for any Rust project — build, test,
and run with `cargo`.

## What this agent provides
- Build: `cargo build`
- Run: run the compiled binary (minimal std-only HTTP health by default)
- Test: `cargo test` (libtest results parsed into structured reports)
- Lint: `cargo clippy`
- Code: file / git / edit ops, `rustfmt` fix, `cargo add` / `cargo remove`

## Production
- Docker build (multi-stage, musl/alpine)
- Kubernetes deployment (kustomize)

## Not yet implemented
- Symbol extraction / call-graph analysis (awaiting a core rust-analyzer backend)
